data.description: There is so much to love about this beautifully updated, ranch offering great privacy!  Improvements within the last 3-5 years incl: a remodeled Kitchen w/ quartz counters, farmhouse sink & SS appls, all new Baths w/ marble flrs, fresh paint, new int/ext doors, Deck, retaining wall, concrete drive & more.  Stunning hickory HW floors throughout make this home really shine!  Replacement windows (2017), new metal roof (2014) & radon mitigation (2020).  Great floor plan w/ 3 spacious BRs incl a Owner's Ste, Living Room & Dining Room featuring a vaulted ceiling & highlighted by a floor to ceiling brick wood burning stove. Comfortable Family Room w/ a wall featuring barn siding. The newer Deck offers the perfect retreat with fantastic views.  .62 acres, backing to woods. Simply move in & enjoy!
